  "detailed_description": "Dodge the bullets, shoot the enemies, defeat the bosses! <br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/702810/extras/banner_retro.png?t=1522196612\" ><br><br>Take to the skies for an endless-arcade shooter that is fast, furious and formidable!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Collect over 200 daring pilots over 20 different terrains.<br></li><li>Change the intensity from Scouty to Screamy, if you dare!<br></li><li>Earn a multitude of achievements <br></li><li>Challenging daily missions<br></li><li>Guns! Missiles! Badgers!</li></ul><br><strong>Get flying now!</strong><br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/702810/extras/shootyskies-octo.png?t=1522196612\" >",
